{"title":"长征——史诗","authors":["胡世宗"],"dates":[{"year":1996,"month":7,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"长征——史诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡世宗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是数十万穷苦而坚定的诗人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀着生存的渴望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与解放的畅想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"集体撰写的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一部巨型史诗呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何其长——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两万五千行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这众多的诗人热情而豪放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把自己的生命和血浆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化做掷地有声的诗句"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旋律高亢，节奏铿锵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"待到史诗问世时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大量作者都成了佚名者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有许许多多名字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四周镶上了沉沉的黑框"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果把这卷史诗铺展开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可以从江西瑞金"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直铺到陕北吴起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"气势恢宏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似大江浩荡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遵义城、赤水河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滔滔的金沙江"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大雪山、水草地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悬铁索的桥梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一章一章又一章"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"章章经过铁锤烈火斟酌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经过枪林弹雨推敲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮烈而激昂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在中国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女老幼都晓得这部史诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像晓得传唱千载的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“床前明月光”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它可不是《静夜思》"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它昭示人类"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在最沉的暗夜里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看到希望的曙光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它使人们惊奇地发现"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人可以怎样坚韧顽强"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在征服和战胜前进阻力时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能迸发出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么巨大的能量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间的狂浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可以卷走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一万本平庸之作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可以把那些光耀一时的赝品"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全部彻底地埋葬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而这部史诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却经得起大浪淘沙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它是真正的金子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间越长"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越闪射出夺目的光芒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这无形的巨著"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已不仅仅属于中国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它早已成为全人类的宝藏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我们这颗星球上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它不是滞销书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它拥有庞大的读者群"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各种肤色各种语言的朋友"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正是通过它"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"了解中国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"了解东方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"了解华夏子孙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历程的悲壮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"了解什么是自私的卑怯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么是真正的荣光"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}